3. Recommendations
	1.	Patch & Upgrade
	•	Ensure the agent is updated to the latest version to incorporate security patches.
	2.	Secure Configuration
	•	Restrict agent communication to authorized management servers.
	•	Implement TLS encryption for data in transit.
	3.	Access Controls
	•	Limit administrative access to the agent.
	•	Use role-based access controls within the Tripwire Enterprise console.
	4.	Monitoring & Logging
	•	Enable detailed logging for agent activities.
	•	Regularly review logs for unauthorized or anomalous activities.